<D>__{everybody but one. i don't know you.}
<C>__{haven}
<D>__{what's your name? you seem to be a pretty clever fellow.}
<C>__{orville}
<D>__{orville weekly, and i can't be a total blank. i been here six years and i ain't dead yet.}
<C>__{haven}
<D>__{have you got a vacant room?}
